title: Wurm Unlimited No steam
description:
Custom client for Wurm Unlimited allows you to play on our server without steam. Server is 8x skill gain and 5x action timer. Modded server running priest mod, boat mod, bounty mod, dig like mining, meditation mod, harvest helper mod, and a few others. It runs on a dedicated dual i7 box with 99.9% uptime, database backups twice daily and very active gm's.

Hope to see you in the server!!
